\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Data availability is constrained primarily by information on job tenure.
 For the EU,
 Eurostat reports quarterly figures since 2008Q1.
 Since 2010Q1,
 Eurostat also started publishing data on gross flows,
 which allows us to compare our method with flow rates calculated from gross flows directly.
 We present results for the United Kingdom as an example.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Long time series for job tenure and stocks are available for Canada,
